{"tid":941472,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喪禮先黎喊係冷血","createTime":"2018-12-14T20:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T21:56:41.000Z","uid":117228,"like":2,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7f1a7b333a807d93103510bae55bf1966308758f","tid":941472,"uid":117228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T20:03:07.000Z","msg":"唔計意外死，正常 親近嘅人生老病死嘅話點都會知道佢近況，曾經噓寒問暖，然後接受死訊難過完傷心完先再出席喪禮。<br />\n<br />\n喪禮先黎喊即係事前無關心過然後覺得死訊突然接受唔到所以喊<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母你無關心過人咁撚冷血就慳番啲眼淚仆街含撚死啦！"},{"pid":"62860a079e969414990e73da7e4efa215c5fa56b","tid":941472,"uid":215700,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T20:05:44.000Z","msg":"你都on9"},{"pid":"2164cab4d80c36f050ebbc53c2ee62b9194dbc97","tid":941472,"uid":117228,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"62860a079e969414990e73da7e4efa215c5fa56b","tid":941472,"uid":215700,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T20:05:44.000Z","msg":"你都on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T20:07:47.000Z","msg":"我on9 代表佢唔係冷血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3a9cb798ec401e326b1239fe6bc2bd717a1d3f","tid":941472,"uid":117228,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"62860a079e969414990e73da7e4efa215c5fa56b","tid":941472,"uid":215700,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T20:05:44.000Z","msg":"你都on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T20:14:05.000Z","msg":"呀問心有愧san<br />\n你去出席<br />\n主人家冇喊<br />\n親戚朋友冇喊<br />\n同事冇喊<br />\n得你喊<br />\n代表咩<br />\n佢地好冷血？冇人性？好忍得唔喊？<br />\n<br />\n人地喊撚完啦！接受左喇！<br />\n<br />\n咁仲問心無愧？？"},{"pid":"f8e3ac780333f5bd2b2444630878db1bc8c1a807","tid":941472,"uid":166827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T20:15:13.000Z","msg":"而家傷心喊都唔得 咁惡㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9faebc